'''Nevafilm''' ({{lang-rus|<U+041D><U+0435><U+0432><U+0430><U+0444><U+0438><U+043B><U+044C><U+043C>}}) is Russian production that was founded in 1992, a year after the dissolution of the [[Soviet Union]]. The company is based in [[Saint Petersburg]] with 2 branches in [[Moscow]] and [[Kiev]]. The company does dubbing in both Russian and Ukrainian.<ref>[http://www.digitalcinemareport.com/Russia-digital-cinema-exhibition-statistics-2009-Nevafilm Nevafilm Research on Digital Cinema in Russia]</ref>



==History==
Nevafilm was founded in April 1992. Films were dubbed into Russian with commission from Russian distributors, but in 1994, it was given commission by American company [[Disney]] to have its material dubbed in Russian.

==Clients==
* [[Disney Character Voices International]]
* [[Warner Bros.]]
* [[CTC (TV channel)|CTC]]

==Content==
* ''[[Phineas and Ferb]]'' (season 2)
* ''[[Toy Story 3]]''
* ''[[TaleSpin]]''
* ''[[Monsters, Inc.]]''

